      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IDEAL TIGER NZ (5) was in the money two runs ago then went well again last time over 1660m at this track, finishing 1.2 metres from the winner in third. It doesn't get any easier but on his best form he is capable of another big performance. SPORTY AZZ (8) is in good form at present. Finished second at his latest appearance over 1850m at Marburg, beaten a head. No harm in drawing here with the sprint lane to rely upon and a big run is on the cards. MISS HATTIE (7) comes right into contention after scoring last start by one metre at Redcliffe over 1780m. Top-three candidate. ROCKNROLL DA GAMA (10) is worth plenty of thought off a last-start win by 3 metres at Redcliffe over 1780m.",
